ro.utcluj.bpel
Class QoSModel

java.lang.Object
  ro.utcluj.bpel.QoSModel

public class QoSModel
extends java.lang.Object

A simple QoS model for Web Services. It contains the following QoS properties:

  • Response time
  • Cost
  • Rating

Author:
Florin Pop
